events.name: New York Knicks at Milwaukee Bucks

headlines.description: — Giannis Antetokounmpo had 35 points and 10 assists, Damian Lillard added 28 points, and the Milwaukee Bucks beat the New York Knicks 146-122 on Tuesday night to reach the semifinals of the NBA's inaugural In-Season Tournament.
headlines.shortLinkText: Antetokounmpo, Bucks breeze past Knicks 146-122, into semifinals of In-Season Tournament

events.name: Phoenix Suns at Los Angeles Lakers

headlines.description: — LeBron James scored 15 of his 31 points in the fourth quarter, and the Los Angeles Lakers secured the last semifinal spot in the inaugural NBA In-Season Tournament with a 106-103 victory over the Phoenix Suns on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: LeBron James leads Lakers to the In-Season Tournament semifinals with a 106-103 win over Suns
